 The study will be conducted in two stages.

 Primary vaccination phase: 3 doses Hib-MenC-TT with Infanrix cent -IPV or for the control group a licensed Men-C vaccine with Pediacel cent at 2, 3, 4 months of age; Booster/persistence phase: 1 dose Hib-MenC with Priorix cent .

