The purpose of this study is to demonstrate the non-inferiority of the candidate Hib-MenC conjugate vaccine co-administered with Infanrix cent -IPV versus a licensed meningococcal serogroup C vaccine co-administered with Pediacel cent when given according to a 2, 3, 4 month schedule and the immunogenicity of the Hib-MenC vaccine when given as a booster dose at 12-15 months of age.

